dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights. "Israeli-developed area and refugee camp names do not necessarily conform to BGN recommendations. Boundary representation is not necessarily authoritative." Index of places and key to abbreviations on verso. "300270 2-85." Shows Israel-Jordan armistice demarcation line -- 3 and 25 April 1949. Also shows Jerusalem boundary -- 28 June 1967. UTM grid, Zone 36, international spheroid.
